- This is a Python AI agent project using OpenRouter API
- All LLM calls go through agent/llm.py — never call API directly elsewhere
- Never hardcode API keys — always use .env
- All prompts are stored as .txt files in prompts/ folder — never inline long prompts
- Use type hints in all Python functions
- Every function must have a docstring
- Keep functions small — max 30 lines per function
- Output must always be valid JSON when processing meeting data
